snippet.title: Rolus in the Outskirts DEMO Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the game on Newgrounds
https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/project/4585316
Or 
https://toonyrab.itch.io/rolus-in-the-outskirts-demo

Rolus is a loser who lives in a podunk town on THE OUTSKIRTS of the big city.  He spends his days staring at the wall, shooting at ducks, and dumpster diving for food. One day while looking for a burger, he finds a MYSTERIOUS GLOWING OBJECT, crashed into the dumpster... 
With the dumpster destroyed, Rolus has no choice but to find another means of buying himself a delicious CHEESEBURGER. 

www.cockflash.net
